                <h2>Benefits of Using Data Science</h2>
                <p>
                    Data science revolutionizes the way companies operate. 
                    Robust data science strategies are imperative for businesses, 
                    regardless of size, to drive growth and remain a key competitor 
                    in their industry.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Some of the key benefits include:
                </p>
